<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="407" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="407">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="407">
<bibRefCitation author="Peters, W [CH]" journalOrPublisher="Bericht ueber die zur Bekanntmachung geeigneten Verhandlungen der Koeniglich Preussischen Akademie der Wissenschaften zu Berlin" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="614 - 628" refId="B155" refString="Peters, W[CH], 1854. Diagnosen neuer Batrachier, welche zusammen mit der frueher (24. Juli und 18. August) gegebenen Uebersicht der Schlangen und Eidechsen mitgetheilt werden. Bericht ueber die zur Bekanntmachung geeigneten Verhandlungen der Koeniglich Preussischen Akademie der Wissenschaften zu Berlin 1854: 614 - 628" title="Diagnosen neuer Batrachier, welche zusammen mit der frueher (24. Juli und 18. August) gegebenen Uebersicht der Schlangen und Eidechsen mitgetheilt werden." volume="1854" year="1854">Peters (1854)</bibRefCitation>
does not mention the number of specimens available to him for the description, but later he specified that he found 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“[…">&quot;[...</normalizedToken>
] drei weibliche Exemplare, eins auf der Halbinsel Cabaceira, zwei in Boror, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="während">waehrend</normalizedToken>
des 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Märzmonats">Maerzmonats</normalizedToken>
, in feuchtem Grase.&quot; [
<normalizedToken originalValue="…">...</normalizedToken>
three female specimens, one on the Cabaceira Peninsula, two in Boror, during the month of March, in wet grass] (
<bibRefCitation author="Peters, W [CH]" journalOrPublisher="Reimer, Berlin" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" refId="B163" refString="Peters, W[CH], 1882b. Zoologie III. Amphibien. Naturwissenschaftliche Reise nach Mozambique auf Befehl seiner Majestaet des Koenigs Friedrich Wilhelm IV. in den Jahren 1842 bis 1848 ausgefuehrt von Wilhelm C. H. Peters. G. Reimer, Berlin" title="Zoologie III. Amphibien. Naturwissenschaftliche Reise nach Mozambique auf Befehl seiner Majestaet des Koenigs Friedrich Wilhelm IV. in den Jahren 1842 bis 1848 ausgefuehrt von Wilhelm C. H. Peters. G." year="1882 b">Peters 1882b</bibRefCitation>
: 158). One of the former syntypes is depicted in 
<bibRefCitation author="Peters, W [CH]" journalOrPublisher="Reimer, Berlin" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" refId="B163" refString="Peters, W[CH], 1882b. Zoologie III. Amphibien. Naturwissenschaftliche Reise nach Mozambique auf Befehl seiner Majestaet des Koenigs Friedrich Wilhelm IV. in den Jahren 1842 bis 1848 ausgefuehrt von Wilhelm C. H. Peters. G. Reimer, Berlin" title="Zoologie III. Amphibien. Naturwissenschaftliche Reise nach Mozambique auf Befehl seiner Majestaet des Koenigs Friedrich Wilhelm IV. in den Jahren 1842 bis 1848 ausgefuehrt von Wilhelm C. H. Peters. G." year="1882 b">Peters (1882b</bibRefCitation>
, pl. 22, fig. 2, and on pl. 26, fig. 3, sternum). 
<bibRefCitation author="Bauer, AM" editor="Bauer, AM" journalOrPublisher="C. H. Peters (1815 - 1883). Society for the Study of Amphibians and Reptiles, Oxford" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="39 - 81" refId="B21" refString="Bauer, AM, Guenther, R, Klipfel, M, 1995. Synopsis of taxa. In: Bauer, AM, Guenther, R, Klipfel, M, Eds., Herpetological Contributions of W. C.H. Peters (1815-1883). Society for the Study of Amphibians and Reptiles, Oxford: 39 - 81" title="Synopsis of taxa." volumeTitle="Herpetological Contributions of W." year="1995">Bauer et al. (1995</bibRefCitation>
: 43) consider the specimens inventoried under ZMB 4426 and ZMB 10106 to be syntypes. 
<bibRefCitation author="Frost, DR" journalOrPublisher="Allen Press and The Association of Systamatic Collections, Lawrence" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" publicationUrl="https://amphibiansoftheworld.amnh.org/index.php" refId="B62" refString="Frost, DR, 2021. Amphibian Species of the World: an Online Reference. Version 6.1 (Date of access). Electronic Database accessible at https://amphibiansoftheworld.amnh.org/index.php" title="Amphibian Species of the World: an Online Reference. Version 6.1 (Date of access). Electronic Database accessible at" url="https://amphibiansoftheworld.amnh.org/index.php" year="2021">Frost (2021)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned only ZMB 4426 as syntype and refers to other unnumbered syntype(s) in the ZSM collection. However, 
<bibRefCitation author="Glaw, F" journalOrPublisher="Spixiana" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="153 - 192" refId="B69" refString="Glaw, F, Franzen, M, 2006. Type catalogue of amphibians in the Zoologische Staatssammlung Muenchen. Spixiana 29 (2): 153 - 192" title="Type catalogue of amphibians in the Zoologische Staatssammlung Muenchen." volume="29" year="2006">Glaw and Franzen (2006)</bibRefCitation>
do not mention syntypes of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1854" family="Hyperoliidae" genus="Cystignathus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cystignathus argyreivittis" order="Anura" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" rank="species" species="argyreivittis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="407">Cystignathus argyreivittis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
present at ZSM. 
<bibRefCitation author="Ahl, E" journalOrPublisher="Sitzungsberichte der Gesellschaft Naturforschender Freunde zu Berlin" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" refId="B6" refString="Ahl, E, 1930c. Zur Kenntnis der afrikanischen Froschgattung Kassina Girard. Zoologischer Anzeiger 88(9/10): 277-283." title="Zur Kenntnis der afrikanischen Froschgattung Kassina Girard. Zoologischer Anzeiger 88 (9 / 10): 277 - 283." year="1930 c">Ahl (1930c</bibRefCitation>
: 283) denotes [ZMB] 4426 as 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Typus”">&quot;Typus&quot;</normalizedToken>
and [ZMB] 10106 (two specimens) as 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Cotypen”">&quot;Cotypen&quot;</normalizedToken>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1854" family="Hyperoliidae" genus="Cystignathus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cystignathus argyreivittis" order="Anura" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" rank="species" species="argyreivittis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="407">Cystignathus argyreivittis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This constitutes a lectotype designation of ZMB 4426 from 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Boror”">&quot;Boror&quot;</normalizedToken>
(ICZN 1999: Art. 74.5).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="407">
W. C. H. Peters, a zoologist, anatomist and later director of ZMB (from 1857 to 1883) undertook a journey to Mozambique from September 1842. Via Portugal and Luanda (Angola) he reached Mozambique Island on 17 June 1843. During his stay in Mozambique, he undertook various short trips, e.g. to Zanzibar, Anjuan (Comores), Saint Augustin (Madagascar) and South Africa. On August 7, 1847 he left Mozambique and sailed via Goa and Mumbai (India), Candy (Sri Lanka) and Egypt to return to Berlin in early 1848 (itinerary and map in 
<bibRefCitation author="Bauer, AM" editor="Bauer, AM" journalOrPublisher="C. H. Peters (1815 - 1883). Society for the Study of Amphibians and Reptiles, Oxford" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="39 - 81" refId="B21" refString="Bauer, AM, Guenther, R, Klipfel, M, 1995. Synopsis of taxa. In: Bauer, AM, Guenther, R, Klipfel, M, Eds., Herpetological Contributions of W. C.H. Peters (1815-1883). Society for the Study of Amphibians and Reptiles, Oxford: 39 - 81" title="Synopsis of taxa." volumeTitle="Herpetological Contributions of W." year="1995">Bauer et al. 1995</bibRefCitation>
). Already during his journey, Peters regularly sent his collections back to Berlin, some of which were donated to the Anatomical Museum, the majority was given to the ZMB and a number of doublets (
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Doubletten”">&quot;Doubletten&quot;</normalizedToken>
) were sold (
<bibRefCitation author="Brauer, A" editor="Lenz, M" journalOrPublisher="Dritter Band. Buchhandlung des Waisenhauses, Halle an der Saale" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="372 - 389" refId="B33" refString="Brauer, A, 1910. Das zoologische Museum. In: Lenz, M, Ed., Geschichte der koeniglichen Friedrich-Wilhelms-Universitaet zu Berlin. Dritter Band. Buchhandlung des Waisenhauses, Halle an der Saale: 372 - 389" title="Das zoologische Museum." volumeTitle="Geschichte der koeniglichen Friedrich-Wilhelms-Universitaet zu Berlin." year="1910">Brauer 1910</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Bauer, AM" editor="Bauer, AM" journalOrPublisher="C. H. Peters (1815 - 1883). Society for the Study of Amphibians and Reptiles, Oxford" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="39 - 81" refId="B21" refString="Bauer, AM, Guenther, R, Klipfel, M, 1995. Synopsis of taxa. In: Bauer, AM, Guenther, R, Klipfel, M, Eds., Herpetological Contributions of W. C.H. Peters (1815-1883). Society for the Study of Amphibians and Reptiles, Oxford: 39 - 81" title="Synopsis of taxa." volumeTitle="Herpetological Contributions of W." year="1995">Bauer et al. 1995</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
